A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She has a friend who is a psychic and she asks her friend to do a reading for her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The psychic tells her that she has been dating the same guy over and over again.

actions.text: The psychic tells her that she has been dating the same guy over and over again and that he is a shapeshifter.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The woman is still not sure if she believes the psychic, but she decides to confront the guy about it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She asks him if he is a shapeshifter and he admits that he is.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells her that he has been in love with her for a long time and that he has been trying to get it right this time.

actions.name: text-insert
